title: 2BR/2BA APARTMENT WITH QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Colonnade Apartments!', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', '$3,821 - $4,436', '.', '2 Bed 2 Bath .', '1100 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 735 - Available 08/30/22', 'The Colonnade Apartments', 'Address:', '201 S 4th Street San Jose, CA 95112', 'DESCRIPTION', 'If you are looking for your next home, check out this beautiful two-bedroom, two-bathroom model at The Colonnade Apartments!', 'The elegance of the kitchen comes from the stain-resistant quartz countertops.', 'After a long day, prepare a quick and delicious dinner using the stainless steel appliances.', 'Select models even come with walk-in closets to keep your things organized.', 'The interior also includes vinyl plank flooring, energy-efficient double pane windows, and in-wall USB charging ports!', 'Work on office projects from home in the community’s business center.', 'Make your weekend more relaxing and by visiting the sauna, or use the fitness center to achieve your fitness goals.', 'Other amenities include covered and assigned parking spaces, a laundry facility, and storage units.', 'Speak with a friendly staff to schedule a tour.', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
